Text:
@Nihility1:  I am just starting this download myself, so I can not speak for this particular download.  However, I recommend trying "good reader" for iPad.  I have a lot of large books, over 500MB (mostly textbooks) that will not open in ibooks, goodreader handles them without a problem on my iPad.  

The app can do a bunch of other things that ibooks can not do, as well, like cropping, notation, connect to servers and dropbox.  

With all the iOS apps out there, I know it helps some times to get a good recommendation.  The app works really well.
